title: ‘Selling Sunset’ Episodes 6-10 Breakdown
description:
Juliet Litman is joined by Callie Curry to discuss the final episodes of season five of 'Selling Sunset.' They share their reactions to the lackluster finale, give their thoughts on the new season as a whole, and hand out fun superlatives.
Hosts: Juliet Litman and Callie Curry
Producers: Devon Manze and Chelsea Stark-Jones
